      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SLICK SILAS (3) boasts a strong record this journey here with three wins and four minors from nine tries. Comes off a (18.94) win last time, scoring by a neck in a Grade 5 over 330m at this track. Rates on top and should go close. MINH TOMMY (1) stalked the lead from a middle draw and boxed on well to finish one length back in second (23.08) at Dubbo in a Grade 5 over 400m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Overdue and expected to feature again. LUMEAH MONTE (2) broke a string of placings finishing in the money two on end before a last start fifth (20.16) at Gunnedah. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Leading chance. JACOBITE WIZARD (6) is worth including after a top-three finish most recently.",
